00:31:16.425 --> 00:31:17.633 align:middle line:90%
>> AV: They'd never fell you.

00:31:17.633 --> 00:31:19.501 align:middle line:90%
>> RM: They're too cool.

00:31:19.501 --> 00:31:21.370 align:middle line:84%
>> AV: They're going
to learn to show up,

00:31:21.370 --> 00:31:23.806 align:middle line:84%
they're going to
learn how to surf,

00:31:23.806 --> 00:31:27.109 align:middle line:84%
they're going to learn to
have fun with other boys,

00:31:27.109 --> 00:31:30.612 align:middle line:84%
without killing anybody,
and have true fun.

00:31:30.612 --> 00:31:33.103 align:middle line:84%
So this is how it start,
and I start taking it up

00:31:33.103 --> 00:31:35.684 align:middle line:84%
in the mountains, and
wow, this is working.

00:31:35.684 --> 00:31:38.562 align:middle line:84%
And then became -- then
I discovered there was

00:31:38.562 --> 00:31:43.625 align:middle line:84%
a gentleman, his name is Brad
Leslie, is my mentor in Canada,

00:31:43.625 --> 00:31:46.895 align:middle line:84%
