>> AV: Adventure weekend.

00:31:52.108 --> 00:31:53.101 align:middle line:90%
Coming up 12 of July.

00:31:53.101 --> 00:31:56.305 align:middle line:84%
And he brings, like,
hundreds of kids

00:31:56.305 --> 00:31:59.041 align:middle line:90%
